Dear all,

Please, let me get your attention on the following updated details with reg=
arding to the 6lo Plugtests to be held in Yokohama from 6th to 8th November=
:


-          After receiving some questions about the scope of the Plugtests,=
 I would like to clarify that IEEE 802.15.4 is part of the Plugtests scope.=
 We have updated the Plugtests website (http://www.etsi.org/news-events/eve=
nts/1003-6lo-plugtests) accordingly.

-          Regarding the registration deadline, we have had to change the d=
eadline to 9th October due to some logistic details that need to be prepare=
d in advance as the event will be in Japan. So, please, take into account t=
he new date if you're considering your participation.

Should you have any other question, please, do not hesitate to contact us.

Please, do not hesitate to forward this email to other colleagues.

Best regards.

